sg":"香港淪陷，非法不利，制不善，弊在奶共。奶共而力虧，破滅之道也。或曰：百萬港人，率奶共耶？曰：不奶者以奶者喪，蓋失強援，不能獨完。故曰：弊在奶共也。<br />\n<br />\n支以攻取之外，小則獲地，大則得區。較支之所得，與戰勝而得者，其實百倍；諸侯之所亡，與戰敗而亡者，其實亦百倍。則支之所大欲，香港之所大患，固不在戰矣。思厥先祖父，暴霜露，斬荊棘，以有完善體制。子孫視之不甚惜，舉以予人，如棄草芥。今日西九龍，明日港珠澳，然后得一夕安寢。起視四境，而蝗蟲又至矣。然則香港之地有限，支那之欲無厭，奉之彌繁，侵之愈急。故不戰而強弱勝負已判矣。至于顛覆，理固宜然。古人云：&ldquo;以地事支，猶抱薪救火，薪不盡，火不滅。&rdquo;此言得之。"},{"pid":"a95f9a2c852019b10487c4039f3b27e9cca3aca0","tid":335915,"uid":121844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"合法地違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a893af97cd9e8310874d08db59cff197bec13b2","tid":335915,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合法地違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407d77a8e1a606b3f05494d9cc37a529bbdc6693","tid":335915,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a1d91cbf83ebe6cb06b6d2c25b6d8f9895db07e","tid":335915,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11162d2694c85496f336b71e8c732e728dd95abc","tid":335915,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"小人充斥我港，賣港不遺餘力<br />\n無權政府背叛，人民聲音壓迫"}]}